<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a nǐ shì yáo jiàng, wǒ běn shì yī bǎ ní tǔ.
 zěn néng yǒu zì jǐ de xuǎn zé? zhǐ yǒu wán quán de shùn fú.
 jīn shēng néng bèi nǐ yòng, nà shì wǒ méng le zuì dà de zhù fú.
 ní tǔ néng zuò shén me, dōu shì zhǔ nǐ cí ài de juàn gù.
 gǎn ēn bù jǐn, huān hū bù zhù.
 yī shēng zhōng dōu shì qí jī, yīn nǐ shì yáo jiàng, wǒ shì ní tǔ.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ a nǐ shì yáo jiàng 迦南927</title>
<hymn_number>927</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>